################## LOGISTICS ##################
### Countries
GET {{host}}/{{locale}}/api/v1/countries
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Regions (225 is the ID of Turkey)
GET {{host}}/{{locale}}/api/v1/countries/225/regions
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cities (225 is the ID of Turkey, 34 is the ID of Istanbul)
GET {{host}}/{{locale}}/api/v1/countries/225/regions/34/cities
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Get Supported/Enabled locales
GET {{host}}/{{locale}}/api/v1/settings/locales
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

